T1  - Coordinating with a “Problem Solver”
AU  - Glazer, Jacob
AU  - Rubinstein, Ariel
Y1  - 2019/03/19
PY  - 2019
DA  - 2019/06/01
N1  - doi: 10.1287/mnsc.2018.3078
